show.description:
What if you could see the exact moment someone will die?
Uday Mehra, an ordinary man, has a terrifying gift, he can see a death countdown of people. When he warns strangers about their fate, no one believes him… until a shocking plane crash proves him right.Now, caught between destiny and his desperate attempts to save her lover, Uday finds himself battling time, love, betrayal, and a deadly conspiracy. The clock is ticking. Will he save them… or lose everything? Watch now!
